## 1. Definitions

- **"SDK"** means the ComposaSDK.framework binary, headers, and associated documentation.
- **"Sample Code"** means the source code files included in the ComposaSampleEffects and ComposaSampleTransitions directories.
- **"Plugin"** means a software module (.bundle) built using the SDK that extends Composa VJ functionality.
- **"YouTube Plugin"** means the ComposaYouTubePlugin.bundle binary included in this repository.

